                  , as a piece of good and lawful money and current coin of this realm, a piece of false and counterfeit money in the likeness and similitude of a guinea, well knowing it to be false and counterfeit; and that within ten days, to wit, on the <rs id="t17740216-96-cd485" type="crimeDate">29th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17740216-96-off483 t17740216-96-cd485"></join>, they did offer to 
                     
